### Test with Bubble Sort
POST http://localhost:8000/api/execute/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "n = len(arr)\nfor i in range(n):\n    for j in range(n - i - 1):\n        viz.capture(arr, comparing=[j, j+1])\n        if arr[j] > arr[j+1]:\n            arr[j], arr[j+1] = arr[j+1], arr[j]\n            viz.capture(arr, swapping=[j, j+1])",
  "array": [64, 34, 25, 12, 22]
}

